snippet.title: Destroy All Humans Clone Carnage Gameplay
snippet.description:
Wreak havoc in Clone Carnage! This standalone DLC comes with 4 modes, 6 maps, and up to 4-player multiplayer. Split-screen lets you double the damage in local 2-player multiplayer. Unleash your wild side in Rampage, Armageddon, Race, and Abduction modes!

Reforge First Look is an encyclopedia of first looks at new games, updates to games, DLCs, and expansions. If you want to have input on what games make it to this channel get in our Discord!
